BillTitle: An Act to amend the Divorce Act (equal parenting) and to make consequential amendments to other Acts

votes.ConstituencyName: West Vancouver—Sunshine Coast—Sea to Sky Country

summary: This enactment amends the Divorce Act to replace the concept of “custody orders” with that of “parenting orders”. It instructs judges, when making a parenting order, to apply the principle of equal parenting unless it is established that the best interests of the child would be substantially enhanced by allocating parental responsibility other than equally.
